Emirates Considering $1 Billion Bond to Fund Jets, Al Bayan Says

-- B y   T a m a r a   W a l i d
-- 
2011-09-29T07:49:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-29/emirates-considering-1-billion-bond-to-fund-jets-al-bayan-says.html
Emirates, the largest airline by
international traffic, may issue $1 billion of bonds to finance
plane purchases if conditions are right,  Al Bayan  reported,
citing Brian Jeffrey, senior vice president, corporate treasury.  To contact the reporter on this story:
